name: VR connection
description:
simply ♡ i had a lot of fun making this composition.

words are not enough to describe what i feel when i do this stuff in c4d. 

i think it's the closest thing to a transcendental experience and i hope it inspires everyone who sees it, regardless of whether they like it or not, regardless of right and wrong, the need to create keeps me breathing so thank you very much for that. 


3000 x 3000 pixels 

300 dpi
